snippet.title: Khloe Kardashian Speaks On Tristan Thompson Moving On With Iggy Azalea
snippet.description:
Khloe Kardashian Speaks On Tristan Thompson Moving On With Iggy Azalea

Khloe Kardashian and her on-again-off-again boyfriend Tristan Thompson recently sparked reconciliation rumors and sources close to Khloe revealed the reality star wants to have another kid with Tristan.

But we’re not so sure since according to sources there is something going on between Tristan and Australian rapper Iggy Azalea 

So does that mean Tristan is moving on from Khloe? And how did Khloe react to being replaced by Iggy?
